data.description: Presenting this beautiful residence nestled in the Oak Grove Community of San Jose. 119 Cherry Blossom is a stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. With wall to wall renovations, This spacious and inviting home boasts over 1,500 square feet of living space. In the great room, your new home is perfect for families and entertaining guests. The large windows and multiple sets of French Doors fill the space with ample natural light throughout. The home features a sleek kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, and modern cabinets. Off the living area is a private study for your remote work days. The large master suite with a wall to wall dual closets nestled between the elegant ensuite.. Enjoy the California sunshine in the private front yard patio, complete with paved landscaping and mature tree overhang. And when you are ready to build your ADU, approved plans are already designed for you! Conveniently located near top-rated schools, parks, and shopping, this home is a must-see for anyone looking to settle in Silicon Valley.
